about.name: Prathamesh Sable
about.long_bio: I am a Passionate computer engineering student and experienced programmer, eager to create innovative software solutions. I'm currently pursuing my undergraduate degree at Modern Education Society's College of Engineering, Pune, specializing in computer engineering.    Beyond academics, I lead the developer team at Techverse, the technical club at my college. Previously, I held the role of Campus Ambassador for Geeks for Geeks in 2022-23. My tech skillset spans diverse languages and technologies including Python, C/C++, Git/GitHub, Django, backend web development, and SQL. I'm a driven learner, always excited to experiment with new technologies and confident in my ability to adapt and excel in any project. I look forward to connecting and sharing my portfolio with you!
